00:15:46,403 --> 00:15:49,406
Awak khusyuk melukis di bar tadi.

236
00:15:50,699 --> 00:15:51,533
Entahlah.

237
00:15:52,034 --> 00:15:55,829
Saya lukis beberapa watak kecil,
