saya pandai membaiki kerosakan.

248
00:16:32,533 --> 00:16:34,410
Sedapnya coklat panas awak.

249
00:16:35,035 --> 00:16:36,996
Ia sains, bukan karya seni.

250
00:16:37,663 --> 00:16:38,497
Ya.

251
00:16:46,964 --> 00:16:47,798
Awak ada…

252
00:16:48,549 --> 00:16:50,592
Maaf. Susu.

253
00:16:53,929 --> 00:16:56,223
Duduklah rapat sikit, kalau awak nak.

254
00:16:56,306 --> 00:16:58,559
- Apa?
- Awak boleh duduk lebih rapat.

255
00:16:59,184 --> 00:17:00,019
Baiklah.

256
00:17:12,448 --> 00:17:14,199
Saya… Maafkan saya.

257
00:17:14,282 --> 00:17:15,117
Ya.

258
00:17:22,207 --> 00:17:24,667
- Saya kena jawab telefon.
