259
00:17:24,752 --> 00:17:26,002
Maafkan saya.

260
00:17:26,086 --> 00:17:28,088
Hei. Semuanya okey?

261
00:17:29,214 --> 00:17:30,049
Apa?

262
00:17:30,132 --> 00:17:31,216
Di mana?

263
00:17:32,301 --> 00:17:35,304
Okey. Ya. Saya datang sekarang.

264
00:17:37,514 --> 00:17:38,515
Semuanya okey?

265
00:17:38,599 --> 00:17:43,062
